@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_cdlmfs(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = ((v2 - tmp) + 0.65)
    v0 = ((wp.exp(v1 + 0.63) - (tmp + 0.20 + tmp + 0.87)) / ((v0 + 0.67 / v0 + 0.06) * 0.86))
    v0 = v1
    v1 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
